=========== data
better synthetic data, with realistic vocab scale, but reasonable (10 or 20) number of topics

vocab_size = 10000
K = 20

"cube"
3 faces, each with 2 orientations
= x6 multiplier

suppose we have B bars on a single side
then we have 6*B^2 total topics (assuming all are used)

setting B=2 gives 24 total topics
setting B=3 gives 54 total topics

total of cuberoot(V) words on a side.  if we did V=8000, then side-length=20

