=========== AllocModel
* HDPFull : better optimization for u based on reparameterization of its Beta distr

* HDPFull : full posterior for both v and r
* HDPPE : full posterior for r, 
* HDPFullHard : full posterior for v, hard assignments for r
* HDPPEHard : point estimates for v, hard assignments for r

=========== Stochastic
* better computation of the evidence bound (avg across batches)

